b'     Dear Students,         Link       The onlineapplication for exchange students wishing to study at Hof University during the winter semester 201 6 /1 7 , is  now open . Application Deadline is  30 th  of June 201 6 .    Students apply by using an  online application system.     After the application data has been submitted online, you need to print out the application form. The printed application form must be signed by the coordinator of the home institution and then scanned and send to Hof Univ by EMail.   Please note that Hof Univ cannot process your application without the required stamp and signatures. Students will receive confirmation of receipt of their application per EMail. All applications will be examined and if accepted, a Letter of Acceptance will be posted to the student at the beginning of July.  A stepbystep application guide can be found here:       The orientation program (including IntensiveGerman course) for exchange students takes place from 14.09.2016  30.09.2016, regular lectures start on the 04 th  of October. For further information please have a look at the attached fact sheet . The English taught courses can be found on the   homepage .    </span  &nb;sp;   Mr. Arvind Sivamani  Liaison Officer (Outgoing Students)  International Relations  Office of International Relations l 2 nd Floor, IC & SR Building  Indian Institute of Technology Madras l Chennai  600 036 l INDIA  Tel: (91) 0442257 4928  Email: oir4@wmail.iitm.ac.in   Website:    '

